# CivicSetu environment
#
# Gemini API key — optional. When present, live Gemini calls power the AI
# features (multi-issue vision, worsening prediction, complaint letters,
# cluster root-cause, voice extraction, impact narrative, escalation script).
# When ABSENT, the app runs fully on curated cached responses so the demo
# never depends on the network. Get a key: https://aistudio.google.com/apikey
VITE_GEMINI_API_KEY=

# Optional model overrides (sensible defaults are baked in)
# VITE_GEMINI_TEXT_MODEL=gemini-2.0-flash
# VITE_GEMINI_VISION_MODEL=gemini-2.0-flash
